{"tid":1122492,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱睇apm 830 avg4 個拍手撚我屌你老母呀","createTime":"2019-04-24T03:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T13:29:21.000Z","uid":224994,"like":33,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4e61647a849edec395efc6f0a4a176f1540fe4","tid":1122492,"uid":224994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"你個柒頭皮高潮位拍手都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後一套我忍你<br />\n<br />\n但你可唔可以唔好係又拍唔係又拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開頭你鳩叫拍手都叫有人和應下 去到中場開始基本上無人再理你就好心收皮啦，死毒撚係到扮撚曬野，最衰我坐前排睇見你唔到，如果唔係俾我知你坐邊實屌鳩你<br />\n<br />\n某主角搶手套果時又拍 點知人地下秒就死撚左（其實估都估到，一早講左個手套能量過大）<br />\n<br />\n然後喪禮果幕播緊好沉重既bgm 果時又拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母當堂無曬癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你老母死果時洗唔洗拍呀死傻閪，垃圾"},{"pid":"27845fce1bed172acb363c09b4437f795ad46db6","tid":1122492,"uid":52705,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:45:40.000Z","msg":"你咁樣算唔算劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"c1a26bfba583069ef3620bc6fe140444ca0b5ffd","tid":1122492,"uid":60831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"咁你唔當場屌???"},{"pid":"28e419217845d615ede532314813442e517b1967","tid":1122492,"uid":224994,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"27845fce1bed172acb363c09b4437f795ad46db6","tid":1122492,"uid":52705,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"